rilla.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Carilla</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#ffffff>(10/20/02 5:33 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Hasten Spawn</span><hr size=1> Hasten Bootstrutter (picture): A gnome that wanders Rathe Mountains. Most find him near the Feerrott Zone side. Note that Hasten Bootstrutter wants GOLD not platinum. His spawn point is in the Hill Giant/Cyclops area of the zone close to the guard tower in the Southwest part of Rathe Mountains. If he is not there, look for one of his placeholders and kill it:<br>
<br>
The most common place holder is called &quot;A DRAKE&quot; not to be confused with the other Drakes there, this is the ONLY one called &quot;A DRAKE&quot; Simply kill him and wait 8 minutes for another spawn <br>
Second most common Pop is Maldyn the unkempt druid. He is level 34ish and drops a Ranger Quest item. Again kill him and wait for another pop, one should be kind enough to offer the bow parts &quot;a&quot; that he drops to some ranger for their glove quest of course <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Note that killing Maldyn effects no factions at all. <br>
3rd most common is Hasten, Thank goodness <br>
The most rare spawn is Brother Zephyl for the Robe of the lost circle (Monk Quest). You can either wait for him to despawn (unknown time) or attempt to kill him. If you attempt to kill him, note that he double hits VERY hard (rumors say somewhere in the 300 range) and is red to a level 54. I suggest waiting for him to despawn *smile*.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=groosumunderbrush>Groosum Underbrush</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/10/02 4:04 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Please note..</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Note that Hasten Bootstrutter wants GOLD not platinum.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"> <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :wizard --><img src=http://graffes.netfirms.com/smiley/wizard.gif ALT=":wizard"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  </div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
<!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:maroon;">With a wave of my wand the truth shall be revealed</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>You can give him 325pp instead of 3250gp</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
<br>
I have personally done this, I have friends that have done this, and I have sold the MQ a few times. Never have I seen it not work.<br>
<br>
<br>
Peace.....<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
